		  <td class="forum_boardrow1" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 1px;" valign="top"><div id="message28366537">This thread is for the discussion of <!--link--><a href="http://myanimelist.net/anime/2251/Baccano">Baccano!</a>.<br />
